com.oose2015.group15.invest.user

Class Processor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.oose2015.group15.invest.user.Processor

  • public class Processor
extends java.lang.Object
    Processor computes tags that match a user's preferences, cross-checks them against our tag database, gets back the list of securities that match, and send these to the APIQuerier to get their full market data/profile
